'''Sigay''' is a 5th class [[Philippine municipality|municipality]] in the [[Philippine province|province]] of [[Ilocos Sur province|Ilocos Sur]], [[Philippines]]. According to the [[2000]] census, it has a population of 2,375 people in 408 households.

==Deng Barangays==

Ing Sigay atin  7ng  [[barangay]].

* Abaccan
* Mabileg
* Matallucod
* Poblacion (Madayaw)
* San Elias
* San Ramon
* Santo Rosario

